definition.text: When a TensorFlow.js program is executed, the specific configuration is called the execution environment. The Execution Environment is comprised of a single global backend as well as a set of flags that control fine-grained features of TensorFlow.js.

paragraphs.text: Left click and Edit to enter edit mode and change this text. ENTER to write new paragraphs. ESC to exit edit mode. Then you can use doscs.save to save your changes and app.contribute to send it to the main repository.
